<Title>Slat Spanwise Lower Flexible Seal (Flex Skirts)</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Up to seven seals per wing may be missing.</Para>
<Para>Seals may not be missing in combination with CDL item 57-43-02 on the same slat.</Para>
<Para>For 787-9 or 787-10, seals on slats 5 and 8 may not be missing.  The three outboard seals on slats 6 and 7 may not be missing, and the most inboard seal on slats 4 and 9 may not be missing.</Para>
